  <?dbhtml filename="libxtst.html"?>

  <title>libXtst-&libxtst-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libXtst provides an X Window System client interface to the Record
      extension to the X protocol. The Record extension allows X clients to
      synthesise input events, which is useful for automated testing.
    </para>

